          "If an appliance has one temperature-controlled zone, the dashboard displays one temperature value with its unit for that appliance.",
          "If an appliance has multiple temperature-controlled zones, the dashboard displays one temperature value with its unit for each reported zone.",
          "If a supported appliance reports no temperature-controlled zone, the dashboard does not display a zone temperature value for that appliance."
        ],
        "exceptionFlows": [
          "If a reported temperature-controlled zone has no latest available temperature value, the app displays a defined unavailable-temperature fallback for that zone instead of an empty or misleading value."
        ],
