        "happyFlow": "The user opens the appliance detail page for an applicable Freeze&Cool-capable appliance while Freeze&Cool mode is active, selects a valid freezer target temperature in 1°C steps between -2°C and 14°C inclusive, submits the change, and the system applies and displays the selected target temperature.",
        "alternativeFlows": [
          "The user selects the lower boundary value -2°C, and the system accepts it as a valid Freeze&Cool freezer target temperature.",
          "The user selects the upper boundary value 14°C, and the system accepts it as a valid Freeze&Cool freezer target temperature.",
          "If Freeze&Cool mode becomes active while the user is on the appliance detail page, the system makes the Freeze&Cool target temperature range applicable to the freezer zone control."
        ],
        "exceptionFlows": [
          "If Freeze&Cool mode is not active, this Freeze&Cool-specific freezer target temperature range shall not be offered as the active range.",
          "If a value below -2°C, above 14°C, or not aligned to a 1°C increment is attempted while Freeze&Cool mode is active, the system shall not submit it as a freezer target temperature.",
          "If the appliance does not support Freeze&Cool or does not expose a controllable freezer zone, this Freeze&Cool-specific freezer target temperature behavior shall not be available for that appliance."
        ],
        "acceptanceCriteria": [
          "Given an applicable appliance with a controllable freezer zone that supports Freeze&Cool and Freeze&Cool mode is active, when the appliance detail page is opened, then the freezer target temperature control is available with the active range -2°C through 14°C inclusive.",
          "Given Freeze&Cool mode is active and the freezer target temperature control is available, when the user selects any whole-degree value from -2°C through 14°C inclusive, then the system accepts the value as selectable.",
          "Given Freeze&Cool mode is active and the freezer target temperature control is available, when the user selects -2°C or 14°C, then the system accepts the selected boundary value.",
          "Given the user submits a valid Freeze&Cool freezer target temperature, when the appliance acknowledges the change successfully, then the appliance detail page displays the submitted value as the freezer zone target temperature.",
          "Given Freeze&Cool mode is active and the freezer target temperature control is available, when a value below -2°C, above 14°C, or containing a fractional Celsius value is attempted, then the system prevents submission of that value.",
          "Given Freeze&Cool mode is not active, when the appliance detail page is opened, then the system does not offer -2°C through 14°C as the active freezer target temperature range due to this Freeze&Cool-specific requirement.",
          "Given an appliance does not support Freeze&Cool or does not have a controllable freezer zone, when the appliance detail page is opened, then no Freeze&Cool-specific freezer target temperature configuration behavior is available for that appliance."
        ],
